# 🔥 12. Production Deployment Setup

## A. Environment Variables (Minimal Only)

```bash
VAULT_TOKEN=short_lived_token
VAULT_ADDR=http://vault.service:8200
```

---

## B. Kubernetes Secret Injection

Use:

* Kubernetes

```yaml
env:
  - name: VAULT_TOKEN
    valueFrom:
      secretKeyRef:
        name: vault-token
        key: token
```

