# ⚠️ Critical Reality Check

This is strong—but not “top 1% yet”.

To reach **elite level (protocol-grade security)**, you still need:

* HSM integration (hardware keys)
* mTLS between services
* Secret leasing (dynamic DB creds)
* Sidecar Vault agent
* Encrypted swap / RAM protections

